  "title": "NgClass",
  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"page-actions\">\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/common/src/directives/ng_class.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L10-L158\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.0.0/packages/common/src/directives/ng_class.ts#L10-L158\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common/NgClass\", \"name\": \"NgClass\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"ngclass\">NgClass<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgClass#ngclass\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label directive\">directive</label>\n    \n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label stable\">stable</label>\n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Adds and removes CSS classes on an HTML element.</p>\n<p></p>\n  \n  \n  <section class=\"directive-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>({ selector: '[<a href=\"api/common/NgClass\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngClass</a>]' })\nclass <a href=\"api/common/NgClass\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgClass</a> implements <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/DoCheck\">DoCheck</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/common/NgClass#constructor()\">constructor(_iterableDiffers: IterableDiffers, _keyValueDiffers: KeyValueDiffers, _ngEl: ElementRef, _renderer: Renderer2)</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/common/NgClass#klass\">set klass: string</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/common/NgClass#ngClass\">set ngClass: string | string[] | Set&#x3C;string> | {...}</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/common/NgClass#ngDoCheck\">ngDoCheck(): void</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n</section>\n\n  \n\n  \n  \n<section class=\"selectors\">\n  <h2 id=\"selectors\">Selectors<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgClass#selectors\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <code-example hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading selector\">\n  [<a href=\"api/common/NgClass\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngClass</a>]\n  </code-example>\n</section>\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"inputs\">\n  <h2 id=\"inputs\">Inputs<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgClass#inputs\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n  <div class=\"input\">\n    <code>class</code> bound to <code><a href=\"api/common/NgClass#klass\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgClass.klass</a></code>\n    \n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"input\">\n    <code><a href=\"api/common/NgClass\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngClass</a></code> bound to <code><a href=\"api/common/NgClass#ngClass\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgClass.ngClass</a></code>\n    \n  </div>\n  \n</section>\n\n  \n  \n\n\n  \n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgClass#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-origin=\"off\">The CSS classes are updated as follows, depending on the type of the expression evaluation:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>string</code> - the CSS classes listed in the string (space delimited) are added,</li>\n<li><code>Array</code> - the CSS classes declared as Array elements are added,</li>\n<li><code>Object</code> - keys are CSS classes that get added when the expression given in the value\nevaluates to a truthy value, otherwise they are removed.</li>\n</ul>\n\n</section>\n\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n  <h2 id=\"constructor\">Constructor<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgClass#constructor\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <a id=\"constructor()\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table constructor\">\n  \n  <tbody>\n    \n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">constructor(_iterableDiffers: <a href=\"api/core/IterableDiffers\" class=\"code-anchor\">IterableDiffers</a>, _keyValueDiffers: <a href=\"api/core/KeyValueDiffers\" class=\"code-anchor\">KeyValueDiffers</a>, _ngEl: <a href=\"api/core/ElementRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">ElementRef</a>, _renderer: <a href=\"api/core/Renderer2\" class=\"code-anchor\">Renderer2</a>)</code-example>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">Parameters</h4>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table constructor-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"constructor-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>_iterableDiffers</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-origin=\"off\">Type: <code><a href=\"api/core/IterableDiffers\" class=\"code-anchor\">IterableDiffers</a></code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"constructor-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>_keyValueDiffers</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-origin=\"off\">Type: <code><a href=\"api/core/KeyValueDiffers\" class=\"code-anchor\">KeyValueDiffers</a></code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"constructor-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>_ngEl</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-origin=\"off\">Type: <code><a href=\"api/core/ElementRef\" class=\"code-anchor\">ElementRef</a></code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"constructor-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>_renderer</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-origin=\"off\">Type: <code><a href=\"api/core/Renderer2\" class=\"code-anchor\">Renderer2</a></code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n  \n<section class=\"instance-properties\">\n  <h2 id=\"properties\">Properties<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgClass#properties\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table properties-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr><th>Property</th><th>Type</th><th>Description</th></tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n    \n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td><a id=\"klass\"></a>klass</td>\n        <td><label class=\"property-type-label\"><code>string</code></label></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          \n          \n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    \n      <tr class=\"instance-property\">\n        <td><a id=\"ngClass\"></a>ngClass</td>\n        <td><label class=\"property-type-label\"><code>string | string[] | Set&#x3C;string> | {\n    [klass: string]: any;\n}</code></label></td>\n        <td>\n          \n          \n          \n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    \n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n\n  \n\n<section class=\"instance-methods\">\n  <h2 id=\"methods\">Methods<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgClass#methods\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n    <a id=\"ngDoCheck\"></a>\n<table class=\"is-full-width method-table instance-method\">\n  <thead><tr><th><h3 id=\"ngdocheck\">\n    ngDoCheck()\n    \n  <a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgClass#ngdocheck\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3></th></tr></thead>\n  <tbody>\n    \n  \n    <tr>\n      <td>\n        <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">ngDoCheck(): void</code-example>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters-1\">Parameters</h4>\n<p>There are no parameters.</p>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">Returns</h4>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>void</code></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  \n  \n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n  \n</section>\n\n\n  \n\n  \n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">Usage Notes<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/NgClass#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <code-example>\n    &#x3C;some-element [<a href=\"api/common/NgClass\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngClass</a>]=\"'first second'\">...&#x3C;/some-element>\n\n    &#x3C;some-element [<a href=\"api/common/NgClass\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngClass</a>]=\"['first', 'second']\">...&#x3C;/some-element>\n\n    &#x3C;some-element [<a href=\"api/common/NgClass\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngClass</a>]=\"{'first': true, 'second': true, 'third': false}\">...&#x3C;/some-element>\n\n    &#x3C;some-element [<a href=\"api/common/NgClass\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngClass</a>]=\"stringExp|arrayExp|objExp\">...&#x3C;/some-element>\n\n    &#x3C;some-element [<a href=\"api/common/NgClass\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngClass</a>]=\"{'class1 class2 class3' : true}\">...&#x3C;/some-element>\n</code-example>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - guide/ajs-quick-reference\n - guide/browser-support\n - guide/structural-directives\n - guide/template-syntax\n - guide/upgrade\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common\n - api/common/NgClass#constructor\n - api/common/NgClass#constructor()\n - api/common/NgClass#description\n - api/common/NgClass#inputs\n - api/common/NgClass#klass\n - api/common/NgClass#methods\n - api/common/NgClass#ngClass\n - api/common/NgClass#ngDoCheck\n - api/common/NgClass#ngclass\n - api/common/NgClass#ngdocheck\n - api/common/NgClass#properties\n - api/common/NgClass#selectors\n - api/common/NgClass#usage-notes\n - api/core/Directive\n - api/core/DoCheck\n - api/core/ElementRef\n - api/core/IterableDiffers\n - api/core/KeyValueDiffers\n - api/core/Renderer2\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/common/src/directives/ng_class.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L10-L158\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.0.0/packages/common/src/directives/ng_class.ts#L10-L158\n-->"
